---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HorizontalCard from "../components/HorizontalCard.astro";
import InfoCard from "@components/InfoCard.astro";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";
import createSlug from "../lib/createSlug";

const posts = (await getCollection("blog")).sort(
  (a, b) => b.data.pubDate.valueOf() - a.data.pubDate.valueOf(),
);

const last_posts = posts.slice(0, 3);
---

<BaseLayout sideBarActiveItemID="home">
  <div class="pb-12 mt-5">
    <div class="text-5xl font-bold">Are You Ready? üî•</div>
    <div class="text-3xl py-3 font-bold">
      The Algo-rhythmic Chase Begins!
    </div>
    <div class="text-xl py-1">January 4 - 7th, 2025 <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> "Anywhere on Earth"</div>
    <hr class="my-4" />
    <div class="py-2 text-justify">
      <text class="text-lg">
Iris returns to take you to an exciting algorithmic voyage this winter. With over <b>1000+ registrations</b> pouring in our last two editions, the excitement was palpable and the competition more fierce. Be ready to ignite your passion for programming, artificial intelligence and machine learning once again.
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="py-2 text-justify">
      <text class="text-lg">
The beauty of LogicLoom lies in its accessibility. Mentoring sessions are provided to support participants in navigating the challenges, ensuring that everyone has the opportunity to excel regardless of their background. Participants also avail the opportunity to foster their spirit of teamwork and versatility in tackling various challenges as the competition unfolds. The stage is set, the challenges await - let's soar to new heights together and make it a booming success once againnnn üí•
</text>
    </div>
  
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold"><i class="fa fa-bullhorn" aria-hidden="true"></i> Announcements</div>

    <div class="divider my-0"></div>

    <InfoCard
      title="Registration"
      img="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/6857/6857461.png"
      sub="Contest, Workshop"
      desc="Registration is live at margazhi.iitmparadox.org"
      url="/register"
      badge="NEW"
      target="_self"
    />

    <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-2">What's in store for this Winter <i class="fa fa-bomb" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="AlgoX Compete"
    img="https://d2908q01vomqb2.cloudfront.net/c5b76da3e608d34edb07244cd9b875ee86906328/2021/08/04/AdobeStock_203293749.jpeg"
    desc="A Machine Learning contest tackling a challenging real-world NLP problem. This isn't just another hackathon, we celebrate ML here. Participants will truly understand the essence once they join us."
    url="/rules"
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  <HorizontalCard
    title="Workshops"
    img="/workshop.png"
    desc="Whether you're new to the field or already have some understanding, these sessions led by top experts from academia and industry will offer an immersive learning experience, packed with industry insights and practical knowledge."
    url="/speakers"
    loading="lazy"
  />

    <div class="py-8">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Past Winners üèÜ</div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-8">
            
            <div class="flex justify-center items-center bg-yellow-500 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <i class="fa fa-crown text-4xl text-white mb-3"></i>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Edition 1 Winner</div>
                    <div class="text-lg text-white mt-2">John Doe</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex justify-center items-center bg-yellow-500 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <i class="fa fa-crown text-4xl text-white mb-3"></i>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Edition 2 Winner</div>
                    <div class="text-lg text-white mt-2">Jane Smith</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex justify-center items-center bg-yellow-500 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <i class="fa fa-crown text-4xl text-white mb-3"></i>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Can it be You?</div>
                    <div class="text-lg text-white mt-2">Edition 3 Awaits</div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>


  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 mt-28">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="divider">Supported By</div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-10 mt-2 md:justify-around"
      >
        <div class="text-gray-400 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow flex gap-4 items-center">
          <a href="https://www.iitmparadox.org/" target="_blank"><Image
            src="/paradox_logo.png"
            width={150}
            height={150}
            format="webp"
            alt="paradox margazhi logo"
            class="max-w-full md:max-w-[10rem] rounded-lg"
          /></a>
<!--<a href="https://wayanad.iitmbs.org" target="_blank"><Image
            src="https://wayanadiitm.github.io/ml/events/logicloom2/storage/whouse.PNG"
            width={150}
            height={150}
            format="png"
            alt="wayanad house logo"
            class="max-w-full md:max-w-[5rem] rounded-lg"
          /></a>-->
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
